data.description: Fantastic 2bed/1.5bath, corner lot tucked away in the cozy Broadmoor neighborhood. A great use of space, this 2 story condo features downstairs living, dining, and kitchen with breakfast bar and stainless appliances, plus laundry and half bath, new flooring installed in June 2018. Upstairs, enjoy 2 spacious bedrooms, full bath, plus a sizable stairwell landing. Gorgeous exterior landscaping with fenced back patio/ yard. Super cute, must see this one!
